<h2 id="slack-and-further-customizations">Slack and Further Customizations</h2>

<p>If you’ve verified the above is complete, please work through the following:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Customize your Slack profile (name and/or profile picture help your team identify you)</li>
  <li>Add your GitHub username/profile link to your Slack profile</li>
  <li>Customize your terminal - colors/themes, default directory, aliases, etc.</li>
</ul>

